{"tid":1112042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 審計署：勞工處招聘會成功個案平均得3宗","createTime":"2019-04-17T08:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T03:40:29.000Z","uid":19454,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"74efca0b7567be884083af4d381054fe7773cfbe","tid":1112042,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:10:46.000Z","msg":"審計報告發現勞工處提供的就業服務，在登記求職人數、工作轉介次數及直接轉介就業個案均減少，其中登記求職人數少7成，直接轉介就業個案亦跌4成半。同時，在2016年至18年舉辦的地區性招聘會每場平均面試次數亦不多，平均就業個案只有3宗。審計署指，數據反映求職人士需要已變，勞工處需全面檢討相關服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190417/bkn-20190417110222039-0417_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190417%2Fbkn-20190417110222039-0417_00822_001.html&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdAr8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=4c1db2a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190417/bkn-20190417110222039-0417_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"22ab5bb6f9eaa3d98a00a06a1b34c9258a27614e","tid":1112042,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef1e237bfadcdfc787eda74352d23571118b21c","tid":1112042,"uid":37661,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:12:50.000Z","msg":"唔閪嘅工都唔會登喺勞工處<br />\n<br />\n有閪人見咩。"},{"pid":"09b4baddb4e576a419e22b8ba056d58f62cb99dc","tid":1112042,"uid":113626,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"2ef1e237bfadcdfc787eda74352d23571118b21c","tid":1112042,"uid":37661,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:12:50.000Z","msg":"唔閪嘅工都唔會登喺勞工處<br />\n<br />\n有閪人見咩。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:14:33.000Z","msg":"jobsdb已經係low-mid range job<br />\n勞工處直頭係地底泥既